@terziele, normally when an issue is already assigned to someone (see the upper right corner of this issue), we don't submit a PR for the issue without first asking permission since the assignee may have already begun work on the issue.

In light of the fact that you have already submitted a thorough PR (#2543), I am removing @mmerdes as the assignee.

@mmerdes, I hope this is OK with you and that you have not already started working on it.
